// GREEN LED ON PB3
// DAC on PA4, DAC1_OUT1 (Labelled A3 on stm32l432 Nucleo board)
// ADC on PA3, ADC1_IN8  (Labelled A2 on stm32l432 Nucleo board)
// Will use Timer 2 to trigger ADC conversions and enable interrupts
// end of conversion.

